title: EYL #118 Earn Your 85 feat. Karlous Miller & Chad Oubre
itunes:title: EYL #118 Earn Your 85 feat. Karlous Miller & Chad Oubre
description:
The 85 South Show has grown from a comedy crew into a full-fledged media powerhouse. They have one of the top podcasts in the world and their shows have over a million views per week on YouTube. They have a production studio, a thriving Merch collection, a packed touring calendar, and a podcast production network. 


On episode 118, we sat down with one of the stars of 85 South and one of the funniest people on the planet Karlous Miller, and the head of business operations for the company Chad Oubre, for insight into the world of media, comedy, content creation, and ownership.
